#: ../../source/admin/monitoring.rst:93
msgid "``/usr/share/awstats/tools/awstats_updateall.pl now``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/admin/monitoring.rst:95
msgid ""
"Please note that load balancers (such as Amazon's ELB) might interfer "
"with the ``LogFormat``.  To start troubleshooting errors such as "
"``AWStats did not find any valid log lines that match your LogFormat "
"parameter``, you might need to bump up the value of "
"``NbOfLinesForCorruptedLog`` in the config files and re-try while you "
"interate on your Apache and AWStats config."
msgstr ""

